\toc2 PILIPAI 
\toc1 PILIPAI 
\mt1 PILIPAI  
\ip Fr Nagai Tabo, Peter Wickham, Gamelai Passi, Kaba Noah, James Rice 1987 MER  
\c 2  
\d MIZMIZ 2 NOSIK 1-11  
\p
\v 1 Ableglam wa netat Kerisoi doge abra upiatidar, ableglam abi omaride wabi dasesaderda, ableglam wa Lamar Zogoge uridli, ableglam waba lag a omar,  
\v 2 wa no netat idonige uridwa, wa no netat omarge uridwa, wa no netat mirge uridwa. Kai sererge iako nawer.  
\v 3 Wa nole lu darakepwararwem wabi auspirem, aukaise wabialam.  
\v 4 Netatnetat wabialam wa nole wabu bakepwararwem, wage no wader le ge ko turidwa.  
\v 5 Able tonartonar uridwa mokakalam Keriso Iesura tonar:  
\v 6 E agekar Agud dawer ege nole ekerer e Agud dali.  
\v 7 Ege tababu bakekri nogleise, akaida mokakalam memegle, eosmeda le noge.  
\v 8-9 Moige le noge, e tababu bakekri ege laglag dawer able eud - able piripiri aukaka nei tumem gair nei.  
\v 10 Ableglam gair legize tabara kokni wairapare Iesuim, moige kotorge, tumem able gesepge, a moige able gesepge.  
\v 11 A gair le ia obatkaret Iesu Keriso e Ople dali, Agud Babi zorom.   
\c 4  
\d MIZMIZ 4 NOSIK 4-9  
\p
\v 4 Wa no sererge uridwa Ople doge gair kerkerge. Kai iako koka dataute: wa sererge baprekrawem!  
\v 5 Wa no uridwa wader leem debele. Ople pe maike dali.  
\v 6 Wa nole wader lu darakepwarawem ege no wabi erkepasamu, Agudi damsawem nalu wa laglag; gair amos waba wanagri no eswaukem.  
\v 7 Ia waiakai Agudi mapodange Iesu Kerisoi doge. Agudira mapodan au sikak wadikedawa pe nalu dike wabi idonige dike.  
\v 8 Mop maike kara mir, buai: nalu lu pe nagri agekar, nalu lu pe nagri amrem, nalu lu pe nagri barkak, nalu lu pe nagri puipikak a zogozogo, nalu lu pe nagri audebele, a nalu barkak lu wage darauspirawem - wa no able lu darakepwarawem.  
\v 9 Wa ge mena gair lu ikerarwem wa karialam berwerda a wage tadasmerda a tasorda kaka tikerer. Ege Agudide mapodan  
\d PILIPAI MIZMIZ 4 NOSIK 12-20   
\p
\v 12 Kaka wanali mokakalam lukak le a mokakalam able mitkar luglug le. Ka geka teberweri able gumik mapodanira ka nawer gair tonar utebge; lewer aroaro, lewer arokak; mitkar a nolekarge.  
\v 13 Ka umele gair lu akere Kerisoi doge pe kari kelar naiswerli.  
\v 14 Mena bakedida wa debele urder wa kara beber wa ikaidarda perper baida.  
\v 15 Wa Pilipaira le umele uridli able kikem kerkerge able debe mirira, ka Masedonialam bakiamuda, ege no wabi zogometade kari upinatida, kari neisweri a kage irpi.  
\v 16 Nade ka mena geka nawer Tesalonikage wage karim upiatidar emarikdarda neis kerkerge, ge kaka laglag nawer.  
\v 17 Ka nole koka lugem dasmeli; kape no laglag nali ka wabi auspireda ableglam wa aiswereda.  
\v 18 Ka kemerkemer bodomalam erpeida a dadgiko. Kara aumitkar nagri ableglam Epaprodaitaside kari neisweri able lu ge wawa temarikdarda. Pe nagri werteda debelaglag zegurlu.  
\v 19 Kari Agudide mari gair lu wanaiswer nalu ma laglag taba zoromlam moige Iesu Kerisoi doge.  
\v 20 Abim meriba Agud a Baba able zorom nagri niaiem niaikarem.   